  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Gparted</title>

    <para>
      Gparted is the Gnome Partition Editor, a Gtk 2 GUI for other command line
      tools that can create, reorganise or delete disk partitions.
    </para>

    &lfs73_checked;

